  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097770/extras/467088586d44ca136d0e12c21a55cfff.avif?t=1772418678\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >War of Paragons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A war for world dominion waged by \"paragons\", the representatives of their races.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once, it was the human paragon who won the war, damning elvenkind to the fate of slavery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A thousand years has passed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another War of Paragons is about to begin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finne, the protagonist of this tale, was chosen to represent humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, her blood hides a secret. She's only half human――and half elf.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will she betray her fatherland to save her motherland?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097770/extras/1153ec6d6324afcdccd0713a34fb6261.avif?t=1772418678\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic turn-based JRPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many different endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of costumes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto battle mode for those who are busy</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097770/extras/467088586d44ca136d0e12c21a55cfff.avif?t=1772418678\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >War of Paragons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A war for world dominion waged by \"paragons\", the representatives of their races.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once, it was the human paragon who won the war, damning elvenkind to the fate of slavery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A thousand years has passed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another War of Paragons is about to begin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finne, the protagonist of this tale, was chosen to represent humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, her blood hides a secret. She's only half human――and half elf.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will she betray her fatherland to save her motherland?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097770/extras/1153ec6d6324afcdccd0713a34fb6261.avif?t=1772418678\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic turn-based JRPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many different endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of costumes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto battle mode for those who are busy</p></li></ul>",
